OL,3,CTrial offers glimmer of hope for
OL,4,Cpatients with incurable brain cancer
OL,6,FThe first patients with a deadly and
OL,7,Fincurable form of brain cancer have
OL,8,Fbeen enrolled in a trial that could
OL,9,Fpave the way for personalised
OL,10,Ftreatments for the disease that could
OL,11,Fone day lead to effective treatments.
OL,13,FThe research being conducted could one
OL,14,Fday allow medics to predict effective
OL,15,Fdrugs for each person, experts suggest.
OL,17,FIt comes as a study highlighted
OL,18,Fdifferences in how genes are activated
OL,19,Fin glioblastoma cells compared to
OL,20,Fhealthy brain cells, a process that is
OL,21,Funique for each individual.
