OL,3,CTrial offers glimmer of hope for
OL,4,Cpatients with incurable brain cancer
OL,6,FIt is hoped that 200 people could
OL,7,Feventually take part over the next
OL,8,Ffive years.
OL,10,FPatients will have their healthy cells
OL,11,Fcompared with cancerous ones to look
OL,12,Ffor unusually activated or repressed
OL,13,Fgenes, which could one day be targeted
OL,14,Fwith new or repurposed drugs.
OL,16,FMax Vardy, from Surrey, was diagnosed
OL,17,Fwith the disease at the age of 24 last
OL,18,FJune.
