OL,4,Cpatients with incurable brain cancer
OL,6,FHe has since had six weeks of
OL,7,Fradiotherapy and is undergoing 12
OL,8,Frounds of chemotherapy.
OL,10,F"I have always been a very optimistic
OL,11,Fperson, however, when I was told that
OL,12,Fmy glioblastoma was terminal and that
OL,13,Fthere are no curative treatments
OL,14,Fcurrently available, I was greatly
OL,15,Fsaddened," Mr Vardy said.
OL,17,F"The research at Queen Mary,
OL,18,FUniversity of London gives people like
OL,19,Fme grounds for hope that there may be
OL,20,Fan effective treatment being developed.
