OL,4,Cpatients with incurable brain cancer
OL,6,F"Even if not in time for me, then for
OL,7,Fthe future generations that must fight
OL,8,Fthis difficult to cure condition. It
OL,9,Fis so encouraging to see researchers
OL,10,Fstriving for a cure."
OL,12,FThe trial comes as research, published
OL,13,Fin BMC Biology, explored the role of
OL,14,Fchromatin in glioblastoma.
OL,16,FChromatin is a mixture of DNA and
OL,17,Fproteins that form the chromosomes
OL,18,Ffound in the cells of humans.
