OL,4,Cpatients with incurable brain cancer
OL,6,FThe study found that a process known
OL,7,Fas chromatin remodelling ` when
OL,8,Fchromatin allows condensed genomic DNA
OL,9,Faccess to certain proteins that act
OL,10,Flike switches to turn genes on or off
OL,11,F` was different in glioblastoma stem
OL,12,Fcells when compared to normal brain
OL,13,Fcells.
