OL,3,CTrial offers glimmer of hope for
OL,4,Cpatients with incurable brain cancer
OL,6,FSilvia Marino, a professor of
OL,7,Fneuropathology at Queen Mary
OL,8,FUniversity of London ` who led the
OL,9,Fstudy, said: "The research in this
OL,10,Fpaper has increased our understanding
OL,11,Fof one of the methods that controls
OL,12,Fthe activation of these genes and has
OL,13,Fdemonstrated that we can use it to
OL,14,Ffind new gene targets, potentially
OL,15,Fopening up new personalised treatment
OL,16,Foptions for patients."
OL,18,FResearchers pinpointed two "novel
OL,19,Fdrugable target genes", known as Smox
OL,20,Fand GABBR2, which are thought to
OL,21,Fpromote cancer growth.
