OL,3,CTrial offers glimmer of hope for
OL,4,Cpatients with incurable brain cancer
OL,6,FProfessor Marino added: "This trial
OL,7,Fwill not only identify activated or
OL,8,Frepressed genes in patient tumour
OL,9,Fcells allowing researchers to predict
OL,10,Fwhat could be effective treatments,
OL,11,Fbut it will also test these drugs in
OL,12,Fthe lab, giving us an indication of
OL,13,Ftheir utility as a treatment option
OL,14,Ffor patients.
OL,16,F"Although not yet at a stage where
OL,17,Fpatients are to be given the drugs
OL,18,Fbased on their prediction, with
OL,19,Ffurther research we are optimistic
OL,20,Fthis could be available to patients in
OL,21,Fthe near future."
